name: Siegelman Stable x One of None

metadata.description: As a rising star in today’s streetwear culture, Siegelman Stable is a re-imagined racing brand turned fashion icon with an impressive list of owners and massive secondary market demand. With limited quantity being key to its signature style, Siegelman Stable drops 20 of the world’s first fully hybrid hats as a One of None exclusive. Each hat displays a unique thread colorway, while the black base and classic Siegelman Stable design unify the 20 unique 1/1’s.
metadata.name: Siegelman Stable Hat - Yellow
